{"tid":2118033,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"警方以限聚令為由阻止林卓廷尹兆堅元朗站開記招","createTime":"2020-07-21T08:27:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-21T13:34:34.000Z","uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"09d7b7d16bca02cc407751cf5872b76a2ac79d8a","tid":2118033,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T08:27:25.000Z","msg":"今日是721元朗暴力襲擊事件一周年，警方下午起在元朗港鐵站外拉起封鎖線，並廣播呼籲市民不要聚集，站內有大量防暴警員戒備。 <br />\n<br />\n民主黨立法會議員林卓廷及尹兆堅在元朗港鐵站外召開記者會，警方以限聚令為由阻止，雙方一度推撞。警員其後將林卓廷及尹兆堅帶到一旁，雙方理論期間不時口角。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2348253\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2348253&d=PhzZiar3PrZ%2B4r6hY23Rj6GvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=db49da68\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2348253</a>"},{"pid":"2e048e70117135e0ce380bba9ada1db85b735ebb","tid":2118033,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T13:34:34.000Z","msg":"👆"}]}